\c 13 Zvimwe zvakagadzirwa naNehemiya 1 Zvino nezuva iro vakarava mubhuku yaMosesi, vanhu vose vaâ€‘ chizvinzwa, vakawana makanyorwa, kuti vaMoabhu navaAmoni havafaniri kupinda paungano yaMwari nokusingaperi; 2 nokuti ivo havana kundosangana navana vaIsiraeri nezvokudya nemvura, asi vakaripira Bharamu kuti avatuke; asi Mwari wedu akashandura kutuka akakuita kuropafadza. 3 Zvino vakati vanzwa murau, vakaraura vanhu vazhinji vose vakanga vakavengana navaIsiraeri. 4 Zvino izvi zvisati zvaitwa, Eriashibhi mupristi, akanga aitwa mutariri wamakamuri eimba yaMwari wedu, wakashamwaridzana naTobhia, 5 akamugadzirira kamuri huru pavaichengeta kare zvipiriso zvoupfu, nezvinonhuwira, nemidziyo, nezvegumi nezviyo, nezvewaini, nezvamafuta, zvakanga zvarairwa kuti zvipiwe vaRevhi, navaimbi, navarindi vemikova, nezvipiriso zvaitsaurirwa vapristi. 6 Asi nenguva iyo yose ini ndakanga ndisipo paJerusaremu; nokuti negore ramakumi matatu namaviri raAritashasita mambo weBhabhironi, ini ndakaenda kuna mambo; zvino mamwe mazuva akati apfuura ndikakumbira kuna mambo, 7ndikasvika Jerusaremu, ndikanzwa zvakaipa zvakanga zvaitwa naEriashibhi, kuti wakanga agadzirira Tobhia kamuri paruvazhe rweimba yaMwari. 8 Ndikava neshungu kwazvo; saka ndakarashira kunze kwekamuri nhumbi dzose dzaTobhia. 9 Ipapo ndakaraira vakanatsa makamuri; ndikadzoseramozve midziyo yeimba yaMwari, pamwechete nezvipiriso zvoupfu nezvinonhuwira. 10 Ndikaona kuti vaRevhi vakanga vasina kupiwa migove yavo; naizvozvo vaRevhi navaimbi, vaibata basa, vakanga vatizira mumwe nomumwe kumunda wake. 11 Ipapo ndakaita nharo navatariri,
